metimes, and with a lot of complex qualifications and subjectivity.</li>=09=
<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You quit immediately for the private sect=
or.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You hang out a shingle adverti=
