istle-blowers. =E2=80=A6</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Because Thomas is =
often among the few people who know about the clandestine risks that his cl=
ients undertake, and about the secret windfalls they receive, he can occasi=
onally act like their therapist or priest, giving them the faith to perseve=
