c gantlet they face. =E2=80=9CHe=E2=80=99s the architect of the Matrix,=E2=
=80=9D the whistle-blower said. =E2=80=9CJordan Thomas built this machine.=
=E2=80=9D ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Because he works on contingen=
cy, his fee is a significant chunk of any rewards that his clients receive.=
 When the S.E.C. announced, in 2018, that in the Merrill Lynch case it woul=
